{"tid":1950841,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"小島製作確診新冠肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-30T14:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T17:58:53.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bd4e1e77bceb79812cdaceadfe2a4dcbabbbe8","tid":1950841,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小島製作員工確診新冠肺炎 將關閉辦公室改採在家工作並針對員工進行健康管理<br />\n<br />\n由小島秀夫領軍的小島製作（Kojima Productions）今（30）日宣布，旗下有員工感染了新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n島製作官方公告指出，3 月 30 日確定有一名 40 多歲的男性員工確診新冠病毒。該員工自 3 月 20 日起就沒有出勤，但今天才確認 PCR（聚合酶連鎖反應）檢測的結果為陽性。雖然該員工從開始出現發燒、咳嗽等症狀後就沒有出勤，根據政府機關的指示並不需要關閉辦公室。但基於審慎考量後仍決定採取以下措施：<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n    暫時關閉辦公室與進行消毒<br />\n    所有員工在家工作（遠端工作）<br />\n    對所有員工進行全面的健康管理和健康觀察<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n  小島製作表示，在以公司員工與關係人士的安全為最優先考量的前提下，將繼續與相關行政機關等合作，採取必要的預防措施來防止感染的擴大。並感謝大家的理解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=194749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D194749&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2VLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=fa590afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=194749</a>"},{"pid":"f4b2320d55b397c2eee5ada97b978ee290401975","tid":1950841,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"其實呢D 3A GAME工作室係咪個個做到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa39adc40488d1dbdd8dc76067d0f37bc367379","tid":1950841,"uid":58201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />確芝麻"},{"pid":"809b56b13075a653da99eeefdf1fc5690eac64bf","tid":1950841,"uid":140326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新冠你老母！<br />\n支那武漢肺炎呀！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"52e7b1c619ba4e49582667b8424bcaf2cc8b7b29","tid":1950841,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"809b56b13075a653da99eeefdf1fc5690eac64bf","tid":1950841,"uid":140326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新冠你老母！<br />\n支那武漢肺炎呀！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"同巴哈講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}